txt.en: Defeated many spiders in the woods of Laerlad.
Defeat spiders in the woods of Laerlad ([placeholder]/[placeholder])
Spiders can be found in the woods of Laerlad.\n\nYou should defeat spiders in the woods of Laerlad.
You defeated many spiders in Laerlad, making the woods safer for the Woodmen of Blómgard.

Many of the spiders of Mirkwood have departed, but for some reason unknown to you they linger still in Laerlad. You should defeat any spiders you find in the woods in order to protect the Woodmen of Blómgard.
Mirkwood spiders still lurk in the recesses of Laerlad, threatening all those who dwell in the Vales of Anduin.
